### Felbat
On some demon-infested world long ago, a species of bat-like creatures was mutated beyond recognition into the disgusting felbats, which now act as a combination of mounts, spies and aerial assault for the Burning Legion. Their massive bodies are surprisingly agile in the air, where they can safely stay out of harm's way while they assault the ground with corruptive globs of mucus. The horrendous, high-pitched screams of a swarm of felbats has caused many defenders against the Legion running for their lives.
 
___
