> ## Gan'arg
>*Small fiend (demon), chaotic evil*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 12
> - **Hit Points** 13 (3d6 + 3)
> - **Speed** 30 ft. 
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|7 (-2)|15 (+2)|13 (+1)|14 (+2)|9 (-1)|8 (-1)|
>___
> - **Skills** Perception + 0
> - **Senses** darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 10
> - **Languages** Common, Eredun
> - **Challenge** 1/2 
> ___
>
> ### Actions
> ***Wrench.*** Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft. or range 20/60 ft., one target. Hit: 4 (1d4 + 2) bludgeoning damage.
>
>
> ***Cache of Weapons.*** The gan'arg uses one of the following options (roll a d6 or choose one); the gan'arg can use each one no more than once per day:
>
> ***1-High Explosive Sheep.*** The gan'arg releases a mechanized sheep into an unoccupied space within 5 feet of it. the sheep has a walking speed of 20 feet, AC 10, 1 hit point, and no effective attacks. It rolls initiative, and on its turn, moves toward the closest creature, preferably toward a group of creature. It then proceeds to explode, forcing all creatures within 10 feet of it to make a DC 13 Dexterity saving throw, taking 1d6 fire damage and being knocked prone on a failed save, or half as much damage and no other ill effect on a success.  
>
> ***2- Mana Bomb.*** The gan'arg throws a mana bomb within 30 feet of it, and every creature within 10 feet of it must succeed on a DC 12 Constitution saving throw, or lose 1d4 level of spell slots, starting with the lowest spell slot available, and taking 1d4 damage per level of slot lost. Slots lost in this way are regained upon finishin a short or long rest. 
>
> ***3- Goblin Dragon Gun.*** All creature in a 10 foot cone in front of the gan'arg must make a DC 12 Dexterity saving throw, taking 1d4 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much on a success. A creature who fails the saving is also set ablaze 1 minute, taking 1d4 fire damage at the end of each of their turns, unless they succeed on a DC 12 Dexterity saving throw to put it out. 
>
> ***4- Rocket Launcher.*** The gan'arg shoots a rocket. Ranged Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, range 5/20 ft., one target. Hit: 3 (1d6) fire damage, and the creature must succeed on a DC 12 Constitution saving throw, or be incapacitated till the start of the gan'arg's next turn. 
>
> ***5- Recombobulate.*** The gan'arg uses a recombobulating chicken on one of its allies, ending one condition on it and restoring 1d6 + 2 hit points. 
>
> ***6- Magnetic Bomb.*** The gan'arg throws a magnetic bomb within 30 feet of itself, forcing all creatures either wearing metal armor or wielding metal weapons within 15 feet of it to make a DC 13 Strength saving throw. On a failed save, the creature is pulled 10 feet toward the bomb if its wearing metal armor, or loses its weapon as its pulled toward the bomb if wielding a metallic weapon. 
>
