### Succubi
Succubi are some of the best-known demons even outside of the circles of demons and warlocks, and the reasons should be obvious; taking the form of an exceptionally attractive woman with relatively minimal demonic features, a succubus will act as the eyes and ears of the Burning Legion, working variously as anything from an infiltrator to a torturer. The name of their game is information, and using their powers of transformation and beguilement, succubi will infiltrate, commiserate and exterminate. It takes a strong will to overcome the wiles of a succubus, and many a warlock - often young men - will try to summon a succubus expecting submissive fealty, and will find themselves flayed and broken, while the demon quietly leaves with any useful knowledge she can find.

***Enchanting Beauty.*** Famously, a succubus has immense powers of seduction. Even without magic, these demons are charming, and combined with their shape changing, illusions and mind-altering powers, it is rare that their needs are unmatched.

***Hideous Torture.*** Without ever missing a beat, a succubus can go from seductive charm to cruel violence. Utilising a barbed whip, poison or shadowy magic, a succubus has a trained and intimate knowledge of how to cause as much pain as she possibly can.

\pagebreak
___
> ## Succubus
>*Medium fiend (demon), chaotic evil*
>___
>- **Armor Class** 14 (natural armor)
>- **Hit Points** 66 (12d8 + 12)
>- **Speed** 30 ft, fly 50 ft.
