### Ur'zul
Wandering the broken streets and canyons of Argus, the Legion homeworld, one might see perhaps their most hideous and disturbing creation - the ur'zul. Disgusting amalgamations of flesh and souls, originally crafted from the countless millions of eredar souls claimed during the planet's original corruption by the Legion, ur'zul take the form of hound-like monsters with countless faces locked in expressions of horrifying, ceaseless agony, positioned above a nightmarish toothy mouth.  Ur'zul have none of the sympathy or love that these souls once felt; the creatures exist only to spread their suffering.
___
___
> ## Ur'zul
