>

\pagebreak

### Vilefiends
Smart and aggressive, vilefiends are animalistic demons known to roam freely in groups, actively hunting mortals. Spiny and protected by a natural armour, their long limbs and rows of teeth are only their secondary weapons; first and foremost they are corrosive, spewing their acidic blood and bile at their prey in the hopes of dissolving them into sludge. Their bite can be crippling, and can corrode away even the toughest of metal. When damaged enough their blood vessels will burst, with high-pressure acid blood spewing generously.

___
> ## Vilefiend
>*Large fiend (demon), chaotic evil*
>___
>- **Armor Class** 15 (natural armor)
>- **Hit Points** 127 (15d10 + 45)
>- **Speed** 50 ft.
